   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Memorandum to Hermon from Iason. Report to Zenon about the sheep, that they are shorn; about the bear(?); about Herieus the quarry-man, that he has not paid back 30 drachmai; about Noumenios the slave; about Demetrios the vine-dresser; about the receipt to Herodotos, to send it to him, for he has measured out the barley.</ab>
         </div>
